# Operational Guardrails 

Prohibited without explicit human approval:

- production database operations;
- destructive scripts;
- schema, SP, FN or trigger changes;
- fiscal rule changes;
- DFe XML/emission changes;
- PDV/TEF/NFCe/SAT flow changes;
- finance/accounting changes;
- WCF public contract changes;
- broad refactoring in critical hubs.

Low-risk automatic changes require:

- local scope;
- known consumers;
- no critical fiscal/financial/PDV/schema effect;
- possible local validation;
- simple rollback.

